@{LINDENT 4}
@{PAR}@{FG HIGHLIGHT}@{B}cast diffuse Shadow@{UB}@{FG TEXT}@{LINE}
@{PAR}@{B}Casting diffuse Shadow to Image.@{UB}@{LINE}
@{PAR}Reads a portable anymap as input. Writes out an extended Image with a diffuse Shadow.@{LINE}
The output dimensions depends on the source Image size plus the selected shadow offset.
The background color depends on the left top pixel of the source Image.@{LINE}
@{PAR}@{B}1.2@{UB} (26.10.2000)  @{FG HIGHLIGHT}@{I}(c) 2000 by Christian Effenberger @{UI}@{FG TEXT}@{LINE}

